Maintainer: Tyler Morgan-Wall <tylermw@gmail.com>
Description: Rasterize images using a 3D software renderer. 3D scenes
        are created either by importing external files, building scenes
        out of the included objects, or by constructing meshes
        manually. Supports point and directional lights, anti-aliased
        lines, shadow mapping, transparent objects, translucent
        objects, multiple materials types, reflection, refraction,
        environment maps, multicore rendering, bloom, tone-mapping, and
        screen-space ambient occlusion.
